#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/infinispan-client.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "This guide demonstrates how your Quarkus application can connect to an Infinispan server using the Infinispan Client extension."
msgstr "本指南演示了如何使用 Infinispan 客户端扩展，让您的 Quarkus 应用程序连接到 Infinispan 服务器。"

#. type: Title =
#: _versions/main/guides/infinispan-client.adoc
#, no-wrap
msgid "Prerequisites"
msgstr "先决条件"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/infinispan-client.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "A working Docker environment"
msgstr "一个可正常运行的 Docker 环境"

#. type: Title =
#: _versions/main/guides/infinispan-client.adoc
#, no-wrap
msgid "Architecture"
msgstr "应用结构"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/infinispan-client.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"In this guide, we are going to expose a Greeting Rest API to create and display greeting messages by using\n"
"the https://infinispan.org/docs/stable/titles/hotrod_java/hotrod_java.html#remotecache_api[Infinispan RemoteCache API]\n"
"and `getAsync` and `putAsync` operations."
msgstr "在本指南中，我们将通过 link:https://infinispan.org/docs/stable/titles/hotrod_java/hotrod_java.html#remotecache_api[Infinispan RemoteCache API] 以及 `getAsync` 和 `putAsync` 操作，公开一个问候 Rest API，用于创建和显示问候消息。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/infinispan-client.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "We'll be using the Quarkus Infinispan Client extension to connect to interact with Infinispan."
msgstr "我们将使用 Quarkus Infinispan 客户端扩展来连接并操作 Infinispan。"

#. type: Title =
#: _versions/main/guides/infinispan-client.adoc
#, no-wrap
